{"lastModified":1748859110537,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::7b291640-3a6a-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nCosy and sporty, the Sun Odyssey 440 delivers extra comfort and accommodations to facilitate life on board. Numerous options enable you to adapt it in function with your sailing preferences.\n\nCruising in Perfect Serenity\n\nIn keeping with the spirit of the line, the Sun Odyssey 440 is a cruising sailboat designed for off-shore sailing. Its resistance, stability, and secure cockpit make it a faithful companion on longer crossings. Careful attention has been paid to fit and finish and to the level of comfort on board – with integrated ventilation, sound insulation, a well-equipped galley, careful selection of materi-als, an exterior sundeck, etc. – to create living spaces dedicated to the enjoyment of life’s simple pleasures and the voyage, itself.\n\nA Sailboat in Your Image\n\nThe Sun Odyssey 440 offers multiple interior layouts: from the version with two immense cabins and a storage locker, to the version with four cabins, able to accommodate up to 10 people, with two in the saloon. For those adept at gentle, perfect manoeuvres, a bow thruster is available. An optional high-performance mast is available to satisfy lovers of speed and performance. And for long-distance sailors, it is possible to integrate a water-maker, solar panels, and additional batteries. Numerous options enable you to configure your boat in function with your needs and preferences.","blueprint":{"name":"CRANE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::7b291640-3a6a-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::23dab4a0-3a6c-11f0-a020-c799ff82ac28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7b291640-3a6a-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::239cc140-3a6c-11f0-a020-c799ff82ac28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7b291640-3a6a-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::239e47e0-3a6c-11f0-a020-c799ff82ac28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a